201cO Muhammad, live as you wish, for you will surely die. Work as you wish, for you will surely be repaid. Love whomever you wish, for you will surely be\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25153,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/08\/14\/two-rakaat-contemplation-better\/","url_meta":{"origin":34893,"position":1},"title":"Ibn Abbas on Prayer: Modest prayers with mindfulness are better","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 14, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn al-Mubarak reported: Ibn Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cTwo moderate cycles of prayer in contemplation are better than praying the whole night with a neglectful heart.\u201d Source: al-Zuhd wal-Raqa\u0304\u2019iq 288 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0645\u0628\u0627\u0631\u0643 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0646\u0647 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0643\u0652\u0639\u064e\u062a\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064f\u0642\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0635\u0650\u062f\u064e\u062a\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650 \u0641\u0650\u064a \u062a\u064e\u0641\u064e\u0643\u0651\u064f\u0631\u064d \u062e\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064c \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19235,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/25\/hasan-bidah-remove-sunnah\/","url_meta":{"origin":34893,"position":2},"title":"Hasan on Bid&#8217;ah: Innovation in religion replaces Sunnah like it","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 25, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Awza\u2019i reported: Hassan ibn 'Atiyyah, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cPeople do not contrive an innovation in their religion but that Allah will take away a Sunnah like it. Then, it will not return to them until the Day of Resurrection.\" Source: Sunan al-Da\u0304rimi\u0304 98 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0627\u0648\u0632\u0627\u0639\u064a \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34581,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/11\/29\/hasan-allah-commands-pure-heart\/","url_meta":{"origin":34893,"position":3},"title":"Hasan on Tazkiyyah: Allah commands you to have a pure heart","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 29, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Khalid ibn Abi Bakr reported: Al-Hasan al-Basri, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cCure your heart, for Allah Almighty requires the servants to have sound hearts.\u201d Source: al-Taw\u0101\u1e0du\u2019 wal-Khum\u016bl 240 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062e\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u062f\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0628\u064e\u0643\u0652\u0631\u064d\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0635\u0631\u064a \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u062f\u064e\u0627\u0648\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0643\u064e \u0641\u064e\u0625\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e \u062d\u064e\u0627\u062c\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0627\u0